{"tid":2145642,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"法國巴黎電影院東主將「花木蘭」宣傳展板破壞涉憤","createTime":"2020-08-08T06:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T09:41:03.000Z","uid":169112,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9002737101e26b5647a31076b4a63eeffbc84e","tid":2145642,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"隨著迪士尼宣布「花木蘭」會係Disney+推出而跳過戲院上映，法國巴黎一個電影院東主將「花木蘭」宣傳展板破壞涉憤。因為肺炎令到很多電影延期同時很多戲院無法營業，本來期待「花木蘭」的上映可以減輕他們的負擔。結果迪士尼直接跳過戲院在Disney+播放，令他大發雷霆。<br />\n<br />\n劉亦菲：「我支持香港警察你可以打我了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/144468469028857/posts/1884670241675329/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F144468469028857%2Fposts%2F1884670241675329%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=d60fe63d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/144468469028857/posts/1884670241675329/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"1cbba3893999a91b81c96bc21b04f3da13d65520","tid":2145642,"uid":169112,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:56:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/destinationcine/status/1291279337191346177?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdestinationcine%2Fstatus%2F1291279337191346177%3Fs%3D21&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=92aba395\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdestinationcine%2Fstatus%2F1291279337191346177%3Fs%3D21&h=b98cc787\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/destinationcine/status/1291279337191346177?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"8d4472e07bebffe54cdecf3af12fda5c44fa1ce1","tid":2145642,"uid":236359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"成個白衣人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a879f34e20e28064c15ace0d15bad214437d0c0","tid":2145642,"uid":169112,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quo